{"tid":1353254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［光復元朗］不如拉埋建制派議員過黎一齊行","createTime":"2019-07-23T02:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T03:56:36.000Z","uid":49524,"like":98,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6fcff1606f7b0ee060eff638fb3756db1031f804","tid":1353254,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:30:23.000Z","msg":"首先 將光復元朗主題定為控訴警黑合作 <br />\n破壞社區安寧<br />\n<br />\n再正式發出邀請函邀請建制派議員一齊反對暴力事件<br />\n<br />\n佢黎嘅 拉佢落水 對警察士氣有重大打擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢唔黎嘅 可以對外宣稱我地有邀請建制派議員一齊守護社區 但係似乎建制派議員對小市民嘅安危漠不關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外我想問有冇正式嘅搞手去拎不反對通知書？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90b2040d3e84fc519337e8ade7f809ff59746f0","tid":1353254,"uid":49524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:32:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"402d82e04537f5c6b4eaf0423912aa4b67783516","tid":1353254,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:32:54.000Z","msg":"集思廣益"},{"pid":"7b0f2557ff9d3af36559db66e8e92edb9923163d","tid":1353254,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:33:19.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"9043147bf87e872ed81697b8dd97d4dfb94d3318","tid":1353254,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:34:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6eb3beac14b216e098a16d0295bdb90fcd29aa12","tid":1353254,"uid":144492,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:34:25.000Z","msg":"會俾佢地騎劫<br />\n一定要將佢地打成係同警黑勾結<br />\n你唔諗下佢地撐送中撐警做過啲乜？<br />\n你覺得佢地仲有良知咩？"},{"pid":"5252a0f11b273ba1708063c275a10333836e89ed","tid":1353254,"uid":28076,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:35:21.000Z","msg":"佢地一定唔會黎<br />\n話近日遊行演變成暴力衝突就得"},{"pid":"9d2d0fb13903af5b534a2ac3cfab3d7c946aa765","tid":1353254,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB